The paper discusses the deployment of a parallel computing framework (PROOF) on a cluster of computing nodes, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The use of Cloud providers and virtualization is also a key aspect of the paper, which could place it in the sub-category of distributed systems (cs.Distributed Systems) or operating systems (cs.OS). Finally, the paper also touches on scalability and optimization of computing resources, which could relate to scientific computing (cs.SC).
